### üìã Certification Details

#### Product Discovery Micro-Certification (PDC)
- Customer problem identification and validation
- User research methodologies
- Market opportunity assessment
- Solution hypothesis formulation

#### Product Roadmapping Micro-Certification (PRC)
- Strategic roadmap development
- Outcome-based planning
- Stakeholder alignment
- Roadmap visualization and communication

#### Product Prioritization Micro-Certification (PPC)
- Prioritization frameworks (RICE, MoSCoW, Kano)
- Trade-off analysis
- Resource allocation strategies
- Data-driven decision making

#### Product Experimentation Micro-Certification (PEC)
- A/B testing design and implementation
- Experimentation best practices
- Results analysis and interpretation
- Iterative product improvement

#### Product Strategy Micro-Certification (PSC)
- Product vision and mission development
- Competitive analysis
- Go-to-market strategy
- Business model innovation

#### Artificial Intelligence Micro-Certification (AIC)
- AI/ML fundamentals for product managers
- Ethical AI considerations
- AI product development lifecycle
- Integrating AI features into products

#### Product Analytics Micro-Certification (PAC)
- Metrics framework development
- Data analysis and visualization
- User behavior tracking
- Conversion funnel optimization

